{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place cauliflower into mixing bowl and chop <nobr>5 sec\/\/speed 5<\/nobr>. Transfer into Varoma dish and set aside. Clean and dry mixing bowl.","Place cumin seeds, coriander seeds and peppercorns into mixing bowl and roast <nobr>5 min\/100°C\/speed 1<\/nobr>. Allow to cool (approx. 10 minutes) in mixing bowl.","Add chilli powder and turmeric and mill <nobr>30 sec\/speed 10<\/nobr>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula.","Add garlic and onion and chop <nobr>3 sec\/speed 5<\/nobr>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula.","Add oil and cook <nobr>3 min\/100°C\/speed 1<\/nobr>.","Add coconut milk and water. Place Varoma with cauliflower into position, secure Varoma lid and cook <nobr>10 min\/90°C\/speed 1<\/nobr>. Set Varoma aside and stir cauliflower.","Add sweet potato, pumpkin, salt and cashews to mixing bowl. Place Varoma back into position, secure Varoma lid and cook <nobr>10-15 min\/100°C\/\/speed <\/nobr>, or until cauliflower is cooked. Remove Varoma and set aside.","Add broccolini to mixing bowl and cook <nobr>2 min\/100°C\/\/speed <\/nobr>.","Add snow peas and spinach, then stir to combine with aid of spatula. Cook <nobr>1 min\/100°C\/\/speed <\/nobr>. Season to taste.","Serve curry with cauliflower rice and garnish with coriander, natural yoghurt and extra toasted cashews just before serving."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["600 g cauliflower, cut into florets","2 tsp cumin seeds","3 tsp coriander seeds","½ - 1 tsp black peppercorns, to taste","1 tsp chilli powder","¼ tsp ground turmeric","3 garlic cloves","200 g brown onion, cut into halves","30 g vegetable oil","400 g coconut milk","130 g water","500 g sweet potatoes, cut into cubes (4 cm)","500 g Kent pumpkin, cut into cubes (4 cm)","½ tsp sea salt, plus extra to taste","50 g cashew nuts, plus extra, toasted, to serve","100 g broccolini, trimmed and cut into quarters","50 g snow peas, cut into halves","80 g fresh baby spinach leaves","ground black pepper, to taste","150 g natural yoghurt","4 sprigs fresh coriander, leaves only, for garnishing"]}],"id":"r101652","imageLink":"https:\/\/3.bp.blogspot.com\/-KQO7WxctkD0\/XZVRQC_A8CI\/AAAAAAAAdL8\/5DozPGmgiiUnm-3o9_wAtUeZS61968S_ACLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_jXRN-4XcqfPCpwg7.png","title":"Vegetable curry with cauliflower couscous","publishedAt":"2016-07-18T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"11 g","fat":"23.6 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"29.3 g","calories":"1663 kJ \/ 396 kcal"},"basicInfo":["easy","20m","45m","6 portions"]}